    <h1>Data Deletion Information</h1>

    <p>We take your privacy seriously. If you wish to delete your data from our app, you can request it by contacting us through the following methods:</p>

    <h2>How to Request Data Deletion:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> Send an email to <a href="mohammed.mohammed.fawzi@gmail.com">mohammed.mohammed.fawzi@gmaail.com</a> with the subject line "Request for Data Deletion."</li>
        <li><strong>In-App Request:</strong> Navigate to the settings page in the app and select "Request Data Deletion."</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Once we receive your request, we will process it and remove your personal data from our system in accordance with our privacy policy. Please note that some data may be retained for legal or operational purposes, but we will not retain any unnecessary personal data.</p>

    <h2>Important Notes:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Data deletion requests will be handled within 30 days.</li>
        <li>Once your data is deleted, certain features of the app may no longer function as intended, and your account may be deactivated.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>For more information, please refer to our <a href="https://www.termsfeed.com/live/85595837-fae6-463b-9a3d-bd7d8d395743">Privacy Policy</a> or contact our support team for any questions.</p>
